Invocation Name: john wooden quotes
des: This Alexa skill will read out loud a single quote from a collection of famous John Wooden quotes. John Wooden is the legendary UCLA basketball coach who won 100 NCAA basketball titles but is also famously known for his collection of inspirational quotes and teachings as well as his "Pyramid of Success". The majority of his quotes were more focused on success in life instead of just basketball.
